Take the blessings of parents.

1276
01:09:40,822 --> 01:09:43,798
Come on hurry up.

1277
01:09:44,383 --> 01:09:46,764
You're the bride and groom,
so show that you're happy.

1278
01:09:46,844 --> 01:09:48,474
