turn out to be such a rascal.

1517
01:25:55,768 --> 01:25:56,938
Who was that female?

1518
01:25:57,018 --> 01:25:59,060
And how did you grow
a beard overnight?

1519
01:25:59,143 --> 01:26:02,217
