1558
01:27:45,893 --> 01:27:47,268
- Let's go, Vikas.
- Leave me.

1559
01:27:47,352 --> 01:27:49,149
- We'll beat him.
- Wear your slippers.

1560
01:27:49,398 --> 01:27:50,460
Hail lord!

1561
01:27:52,852 --> 01:27:54,186
Why didn't Guddu come too?

1562
01:27:54,685 --> 01:27:57,600
