1564
01:28:00,268 --> 01:28:01,519
No, no.

1565
01:28:02,477 --> 01:28:04,477
Don't stand there like a watchman.

1566
01:28:05,852 --> 01:28:07,105
- Sit down.
- Yes.

1567
01:28:09,060 --> 01:28:12,539
